data: Carol Lee is the Founder and CEO of FinTech Solutions, a company focused on digital payment platforms.
Carol Lee founded her first startup at age 24 and has since led multiple funding rounds, raising over $10 million.
Carol Lee mentors new entrepreneurs and speaks at industry events globally.
Carol Lee is located in Austin, Texas, United States.
Carol Lee is active in angel investing.
Carol Lee is interested in SaaS and fintech.
Carol Lee has expertise in fintech innovation and digital payment platforms.
